      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CABAO NICKEL (2) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 20.03 beating Dame Truculent. Has performed well from this box with a win and four minor placings to her name from eight starts. Sure to prove hard to beat. KOTA LAMBAI (1) found the frame for the second consecutive time when narrowly beaten into third last time out (20.25) over 342m at this track. Well placed here and can atone this time. DEEP PURPLE (8) charged out of the boxes with a strong early sectional but swamped late when a close up fifth (19.91) at this track over 342m. Should be about the money. BLUE ENERGY (4) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
